---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="CBD IV Infusion Therapy in Brandon FL | Releaf MD" 
  description="Learn about clinical CBD IV Infusion therapy in Brandon, Florida. Achieve 100% absorption and deep cellular relief under direct medical supervision."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        💧 Cellular Wellness
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">CBD IV Infusion Therapy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Experience maximum bioavailability and deep cellular relief with medical-grade intravenous CBD therapy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Why Choose Intravenous (IV) CBD?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Intravenous administration is the most direct and effective way to deliver cannabinoids to your body's cells. When you consume CBD orally via gummies, oils, or capsules, the compounds must pass through your digestive tract and liver. This "first-pass metabolism" filters out most of the active ingredients, leaving you with only 10% to 20% of the actual dose.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          By delivering medical-grade CBD directly into your bloodstream, CBD IV Infusions achieve <strong>100% bioavailability</strong>. The active cannabinoids bypass the digestive system entirely, providing immediate, systemic absorption to help target inflammation, cellular stress, and chronic discomfort.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Benefits and Use Cases</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Intravenous CBD is highly regarded for its systemic support. It is commonly utilized by patients seeking relief from:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Chronic Inflammation:</strong> Helps soothe systemic inflammatory conditions throughout the body.</li>
          <li><strong>Severe Joint & Muscle Discomfort:</strong> Delivers rapid cellular relief to muscles, joints, and connective tissues.</li>
          <li><strong>Systemic Stress & Anxiety:</strong> Promotes a deep sense of calm by interacting directly with the body's endocannabinoid receptors.</li>
          <li><strong>Athletic Recovery & Hydration:</strong> Paired with sterile saline for hydration, helping flush out cellular toxins and accelerate recovery after intense physical strain.</li>
          <li><strong>Fibromyalgia & Neurological Support:</strong> Offers a non-pharmaceutical option to aid in nerve-related comfort.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 my-8">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Pure, THC-Free Formulations</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            Safety is our top priority. We use only premium, third-party lab-tested, federally compliant broad-spectrum CBD isolates. Our IV solutions are 100% free of THC, meaning you will experience deep physical relief and systemic calm without any psychoactive effects or feeling "high."
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">What to Expect During Your Session</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          At Releaf MD, we provide a warm, cafe-style clinical environment. Your experience is structured for safety and absolute comfort:
        </p>

        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Clinical Consultation:</strong> Dr. Kelly Ennix King reviews your medical history, current prescriptions, and health goals to ensure IV therapy is appropriate and safe for you.</li>
          <li><strong>Comfortable Environment:</strong> You will relax in a quiet, comfortable treatment chair where you can read, listen to music, or rest during your infusion.</li>
          <li><strong>Professional Administration:</strong> The IV line is set by a qualified medical professional, administering a sterile, customized CBD saline infusion over approximately 45 to 60 minutes.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            Read our <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Schedule Appointment
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
